data.eml:eml: Notes on the first instar larvae of the genus Tipula (Diptera: Tipulidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Podeniene, Virginija, Nasevičiene, Nijole, Podenas, Sigitas (2019): Notes on the first instar larvae of the genus Tipula (Diptera: Tipulidae). Zootaxa 4567 (1): 90-110, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4567.1.5
